37 QString StaticFunctions::DBMSDateTimeFormat() {
38 
39  switch(qApp->property("DBMSType").toInt()) {
40  case StaticFunctions::MySQL:
41  case StaticFunctions::MariaDB:
42  case StaticFunctions::PostgreSQL:
43  case StaticFunctions::Undefined:
44  default:
45  return "yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm:ss";
46  break;
47  }
48 }
49 
50 QString StaticFunctions::DBMSDateFormat() {
51 
52  switch(qApp->property("DBMSType").toInt()) {
53  case StaticFunctions::MySQL:
54  case StaticFunctions::MariaDB:
55  case StaticFunctions::PostgreSQL:
56  case StaticFunctions::Undefined:
57  default:
58  return "yyyy-MM-dd";
59  break;
60  }
61 }

63 QString StaticFunctions::DBMSDefaultDatabase()
64 {
65 
66  switch(qApp->property("DBMSType").toInt()) {
67  case StaticFunctions::MySQL:
68  case StaticFunctions::MariaDB:
69  return "mysql";
70  break;
71  case StaticFunctions::PostgreSQL:
72  return "postgres";
73  break;
74  case StaticFunctions::Undefined:
75  default:
76  return "information_schema";
77  break;
78  }
79 }

202 QStringList StaticFunctions::postgresqlFunctions()
203 {
204  QStringList list = QStringList();
205  QHashIterator<QString, QString> hashIterator(postgresqlFunctionsComplete());
206  while (hashIterator.hasNext()) {
207  hashIterator.next();
208  list.append(hashIterator.key());
209  }
210  return list;
211 }

832 
833 EditorTypes::EditorType StaticFunctions::findEditorType(const QString fileName)
834 {
835  QFileInfo fileInfo(fileName);
836  QString completeSuffix(fileInfo.completeSuffix().toLower());
837  QString suffix(fileInfo.suffix().toLower());
838  QSettings settings;
839  if (settings.value("FileAssociations/SQLFiles", "").toString().split(",").contains(completeSuffix)
840  || settings.value("FileAssociations/SQLFiles", "").toString().split(",").contains(suffix))
841  return EditorTypes::SQLQuery;
842  if (settings.value("FileAssociations/PHPFiles", "").toString().split(",").contains(completeSuffix)
843  || settings.value("FileAssociations/PHPFiles", "").toString().split(",").contains(suffix))
844  return EditorTypes::PHP;
845  if (settings.value("FileAssociations/CSSFiles", "").toString().split(",").contains(completeSuffix)
846  || settings.value("FileAssociations/CSSFiles", "").toString().split(",").contains(suffix))
847  return EditorTypes::CSS;
848  if (settings.value("FileAssociations/HTMLFiles", "").toString().split(",").contains(completeSuffix)
849  || settings.value("FileAssociations/HTMLFiles", "").toString().split(",").contains(suffix))
850  return EditorTypes::HTML;
851  if (settings.value("FileAssociations/JavaScriptFiles", "").toString().split(",").contains(completeSuffix)
852  || settings.value("FileAssociations/JavaScriptFiles", "").toString().split(",").contains(suffix))
853  return EditorTypes::JavaScript;
854  return EditorTypes::NoEditor;
855 }
856 
857 QIcon StaticFunctions::iconFromFileName(const EditorTypes::EditorType editorType)
858 {
859  switch(editorType) {
860  case EditorTypes::SQLQuery:
861  return iconFromFileName("file.sql");
862  break;
863  case EditorTypes::PHP:
864  return iconFromFileName("file.php");
865  break;
866  case EditorTypes::CSS:
867  return iconFromFileName("file.css");
868  break;
869  case EditorTypes::HTML:
870  return iconFromFileName("file.html");
871  break;
872  case EditorTypes::JavaScript:
873  return iconFromFileName("file.js");
874  break;
875  case EditorTypes::Diff:
876  case EditorTypes::Commit:
877  case EditorTypes::SVNLog:
878  case EditorTypes::NoEditor:
879  break;
880  // case EditorTypes::NoEditor:
881  // return iconFromFileName("file.");
882  // break;
883  // case EditorTypes::Diff:
884  // default: Q_ASSERT(false);
885  }
886  return iconFromFileName("");
887 }

894 QIcon StaticFunctions::iconFromFileName(const QString fileName)
895 {
896  switch(findEditorType(fileName)) {
897  case EditorTypes::SQLQuery:
898  return QIcon(":/images/svg/text-x-sql.svg");
899  break;
900  case EditorTypes::PHP:
901  return QIcon(QIcon(":/images/svg/application-x-php.svg"));
902  break;
903  case EditorTypes::CSS:
904  return QIcon(QIcon(":/images/svg/text-css.svg"));
905  break;
906  case EditorTypes::HTML:
907  return QIcon(QIcon(":/images/svg/text-html.svg"));
908  break;
909  case EditorTypes::JavaScript:
910  return QIcon(QIcon(":/images/svg/application-javascript.svg"));
911  break;
912  case EditorTypes::NoEditor:
913  return QIcon(QIcon::fromTheme("document-new", QIcon(":/images/svg/document-new-6.svg")));
914  break;
915  case EditorTypes::Diff:
916  case EditorTypes::Commit:
917  case EditorTypes::SVNLog:
918  break;
919  // case EditorTypes::Diff:
920  // default: Q_ASSERT(false);
921  }
922 
923  return QIcon();
924 }

926 char StaticFunctions::rightBracketMatch(const char leftBracket)
927 {
928  if (leftBracket == '(')
929  return ')';
930  if (leftBracket == '{')
931  return '}';
932  if (leftBracket == '[')
933  return ']';
934  return '(';
935 }
936 
937 char StaticFunctions::leftBracketMatch(const char rightBracket)
938 {
939  if (rightBracket == ')')
940  return '(';
941  if (rightBracket == '}')
942  return '{';
943  if (rightBracket == ']')
944  return '[';
945  return ')';
946 }
947 
948 QList<char> StaticFunctions::bracketLeftList()
949 {
950  QList<char> list;
951  list << '(' << '[' << '{';
952  return list;
953 
954 }

1162 
1163 QString StaticFunctions::password(QString pass, bool encrypt)
1164 {
1165  QString pas;
1166 
1167  if (encrypt) {
1168  QChar *data;
1169  qsrand(QTime::currentTime().second());
1170  pas = "*";
1171  data = pass.data();
1172  while (!data->isNull()) {
1173  int seed = (int) qrand() % 9;
1174  pas += QString("%1%2").arg(seed).arg(QChar(data->unicode() + seed));
1175  ++data;
1176  }
1177  } else {
1178  for (int i = 1; i < pass.length(); i++) {
1179  pas += QString("%1").arg(QChar(pass.at(i + 1).unicode() - QString(pass.at(i)).toInt()));
1180  i++;
1181  }
1182  }
1183  return pas;
1184 }
1185 
1186 QString StaticFunctions::quoteSymbol(QString text)
1187 {
1188  switch(qApp->property("DBMSType").toInt()) {
1189  case StaticFunctions::MySQL:
1190  case StaticFunctions::MariaDB:
1191  return (text.startsWith("`") ? "" : "`") + text + (text.endsWith("`") ? "" : "`");
1192  break;
1193  case StaticFunctions::PostgreSQL:
1194  case StaticFunctions::Undefined:
1195  default:
1196  break;
1197  }
1198  return text;
1199 }
1200 
1201 QString StaticFunctions::unquoteSymbol(QString text)
1202 {
1203  if (text.startsWith("`"))
1204  text = text.right(text.length() - 1);
1205  if (text.endsWith("`"))
1206  text = text.left(text.length() - 1);
1207  return text;
1208 }
1209 
1210 QFont StaticFunctions::fixedWidthFont()
1211 {
1212  QFontDatabase database;
1213  foreach (QString family, database.families())
1214  if (database.isFixedPitch(family))
1215  return QFont(family);
1216  return QFont();
1217 }

1698 QStringList StaticFunctions::mariadbFunctions()
1699 {
1700  QStringList list = QStringList();
1701  QHashIterator<QString, QString> hashIterator(mariadbFunctionsComplete());
1702  while (hashIterator.hasNext()) {
1703  hashIterator.next();
1704  list.append(hashIterator.key());
1705  }
1706  return list;
1707 }

7958 QStringList StaticFunctions::phpFunctions()
7959 {
7960  QStringList list = QStringList();
7961  QHashIterator<QString, QString> hashIterator(phpFunctionsComplete());
7962  while (hashIterator.hasNext()) {
7963  hashIterator.next();
7964  list.append(hashIterator.key());
7965  }
7966  return list;
7967 }

8051 QString StaticFunctions::bytesConvertor(QString bytes)
8052 {
8053  unsigned long long num = bytes.toULongLong();
8054  if (num <= 1024) {
8055  return QString("%1 B").arg(num);
8056  } else {
8057  num /= 1024;
8058  if (num <= 1024) {
8059  return QString("%1 KB").arg(num);
8060  } else {
8061  num /= 1024;
8062  if (num <= 1024) {
8063  return QString("%1 MB").arg(num);
8064  } else {
8065  num /= 1024;
8066  if (num <= 1024) {
8067  return QString("%1 GB").arg(num);
8068  } else {
8069  num /= 1024;
8070  if (num <= 1024) {
8071  return QString("%1 TB").arg(num);
8072  } else {
8073  num /= 1024;
8074  if (num <= 1024) {
8075  return QString("%1 PB").arg(num);
8076  } else {
8077  num /= 1024;
8078  if (num <= 1024)
8079  return QString("%1 EB").arg(num);
8080  }
8081  }
8082  }
8083  }
8084  }
8085  }
8086  return "Not known";
8087 }

8904 
8905 QStringList StaticFunctions::explodeConnectionString(QString connectionName)
8906 {
8907  QSettings settings;
8908  QStringList params;
8909  int startIndex = 0;
8910  int endIndex = 0;
8911  QString connection(settings.value("ServerConnections/" + connectionName, "MariaDB:root@localhost:3306/mysql").toString());
8912  endIndex = connection.indexOf(":", startIndex);
8913  //0 - Connection name
8914  params.append(connection.mid(startIndex, endIndex));
8915  startIndex += ++endIndex;
8916  endIndex = connection.indexOf("@", startIndex) - startIndex;
8917  //1 - User
8918  params.append(connection.mid(startIndex, endIndex));
8919  startIndex += ++endIndex;
8920  endIndex = connection.indexOf(":", startIndex) - startIndex;
8921  //2- Host
8922  params.append(connection.mid(startIndex, endIndex));
8923  startIndex += ++endIndex;
8924  endIndex = connection.indexOf("/", startIndex) - startIndex;
8925  //3 - Port
8926  params.append(connection.mid(startIndex, endIndex));
8927  startIndex += ++endIndex;
8928  endIndex = connection.indexOf(" ", startIndex) - startIndex;
8929  //4 - Database
8930  params.append(connection.mid(startIndex, endIndex));
8931  startIndex += ++endIndex;
8932  endIndex = connection.indexOf(" ", startIndex) - startIndex;
8933  //5 - Password
8934  params.append(connection.mid(startIndex, endIndex));
8935  //6 - Connection count
8936  params.append(connection.mid(connection.lastIndexOf(" Count:"), 10));
8937  qApp->setProperty("ConnectionName", connectionName);
8938  return params;
8939 }

8941 QString StaticFunctions::randomString(unsigned int length)
8942 {
8943  QString string;
8944  QString possibleCharacters("ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789 ;.,+¿*-/");
8945  QTime time = QTime::currentTime();
8946  qsrand((uint)time.msec());
8947  for(unsigned int counter = 0; counter < length; ++counter)
8948  string.append(possibleCharacters.at(qrand() % possibleCharacters.length()));
8949  return string;
8950 }

8952 QStringList StaticFunctions::currentEditorTypeKeywords(const EditorTypes::EditorType editorType)
8953 {

8957  break;

8959  return phpKeywords();
8960  break;

8962  return cssKeywords();
8963  break;
8964  case EditorTypes::HTML:
8965  break;
8966  case EditorTypes::JavaScript:
8967  return javascriptKeywords();
8968  break;
8969  case EditorTypes::Diff:
8970  case EditorTypes::Commit:
8971  case EditorTypes::SVNLog:
8972  case EditorTypes::NoEditor:
8973  break;
8974  // default: Q_ASSERT(false);
8975  }
8976  return QStringList();
8977 }

8979 QStringList StaticFunctions::htmlTags()
8980 {
8981  QStringList list = QStringList();
8982  QHashIterator<QString, QString> hashIterator(htmlTagsComplete());
8983  while (hashIterator.hasNext()) {
8984  hashIterator.next();
8985  list.append(hashIterator.key());
8986  }
8987  return list;
8988 }
